 <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-6">Guide Fournisseur Chargeur Chine : Vérification d'Usine et Conseils OEM</h1>
 <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 text-sm text-slate-500 pb-8 border-b border-slate-200">
 <span><svg class="icon-calendar mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M128 0C110.3 0 96 14.3 96 32l0 32-32 0C28.7 64 0 92.7 0 128l0 48 448 0 0-48c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64l-32 0 0-32c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32l0 32-128 0 0-32c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32zM0 224L0 416c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64l320 0c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64l0-192-448 0z" fill="currentColor"/></svg><time datetime="2026-04-28">28 avril 2026</time></span>
 <span><svg class="icon-clock mr-2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path d="M256 0a256 256 0 1 1 0 512 256 256 0 1 1 0-512zM232 120l0 136c0 8 4 15.5 10.7 20l96 64c11 7.4 25.9 4.4 33.3-6.7s4.4-25.9-6.7-33.3L280 243.2 280 120c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24s-24 10.7-24 24z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>10 min de lecture</span>
